a756ddfb-965d-4da1-b8b1-a5420508718a.title: Kaqemeex
a756ddfb-965d-4da1-b8b1-a5420508718a.text: What brings you to our holy monument?

options.text: I'm in search of a quest.

749fa002-dd4e-4ae0-ab5b-c6f490063acb.title: Kaqemeex
749fa002-dd4e-4ae0-ab5b-c6f490063acb.text:
What, personally? No, of course I didn't. However, our
forefathers did. The first Druids of Guthix built many
stone circles across these lands over eight hundred
years ago.

48dec0f2-bb30-4355-ad6a-04d6bf04eb4b.title: Kaqemeex
48dec0f2-bb30-4355-ad6a-04d6bf04eb4b.text:
Unfortunately we only know of two remaining, and of
those only one is usable by us anymore.

options.text: What about the stone circle full of dark wizards?
I'm in search of a quest.
Well, I'll be on my way now.

21ddde13-3f6a-41b6-ab77-eec0ac28db3a.title: <player>
21ddde13-3f6a-41b6-ab77-eec0ac28db3a.text: What about the stone circle full of dark wizards?

e65f1a98-322d-4dcd-bf64-2ba5f7fef644.title: Kaqemeex
e65f1a98-322d-4dcd-bf64-2ba5f7fef644.text:
That used to be OUR stone circle. Unfortunately,
many many years ago, dark wizards cast a wicked spell
upon it so that they could corrupt its power for their
own evil ends.

76b3760a-bf76-47c8-a1ee-8073ae480219.title: Kaqemeex
76b3760a-bf76-47c8-a1ee-8073ae480219.text:
When they cursed the rocks for their rituals they made
them useless to us and our magics. We require a brave
adventurer to go on a quest for us to help purify the
circle of Varrock.

options.text: Okay, I will try and help.
No, that doesn't sound very interesting.
So... is there anything in this for me?

eef8d816-e831-4253-b490-c17c8be5fc3b.title: <player>
eef8d816-e831-4253-b490-c17c8be5fc3b.text: No, that doesn't sound very interesting.

5a4f69ea-f9a0-400c-b056-0990296465ea.title: Kaqemeex
5a4f69ea-f9a0-400c-b056-0990296465ea.text:
I will not try and change your mind adventurer. Some
day when you have matured you may reconsider your
position. We will wait until then.

fa962200-40ee-4441-8826-39d03f8b9210.title: <player>
fa962200-40ee-4441-8826-39d03f8b9210.text: So... is there anything in this for me?

a366b79a-dd15-4f4d-9098-9d43b7426de4.title: Kaqemeex
a366b79a-dd15-4f4d-9098-9d43b7426de4.text:
We druids value wisdom over wealth, so if you expect
material gain, you will be disappointed. We are, however,
very skilled in the art of Herblore, which we will share
with you

9faf0399-d3c9-4137-a64d-988f95b80402.title: Kaqemeex
9faf0399-d3c9-4137-a64d-988f95b80402.text:
if you can assist us in this task. You may find such
wisdom a greater reward than mere money.

options.text: Ok, I will try and help.
No, that doesn't sound very interesting.

57039d7e-5f98-4aee-825d-0de9804db2b4.title: Kaqemeex
57039d7e-5f98-4aee-825d-0de9804db2b4.text:
We are the druids of Guthix. We worship our god at
our famous stone circles. You will find them located
throughout these lands.

options.text: What about the stone circle full of dark wizards?
So what's so good about Guthix?
Well, I'll be on my way now.

003bea14-cc21-4150-b1d1-966fbdd637ad.title: <player>
003bea14-cc21-4150-b1d1-966fbdd637ad.text: So what's so good about Guthix?

5676cac3-e09f-47f5-bdd9-076734b348b8.title: Kaqemeex
5676cac3-e09f-47f5-bdd9-076734b348b8.text:
Guthix is the oldest and most powerful god in Gielinor.
His existence is vital to this world. He is the god of
balance, and nature; he is also a very part of this world.

2a599501-56f2-40d3-ab2b-b8c4a28d423f.title: Kaqemeex
2a599501-56f2-40d3-ab2b-b8c4a28d423f.text:
He exists in the trees, and the flowers, the water and
the rocks. He is everywhere. His purpose is to ensure
balance in everything in this world, and as such we
worship him.

6fc36c02-caee-42a0-9edb-61e2f6a887d5.title: Kaqemeex
6fc36c02-caee-42a0-9edb-61e2f6a887d5.text:
Some day when your mind achieves enlightenment you
will see the true beauty of his power.

816341fe-2d74-4c40-8295-d728dac4f471.title: <player>
816341fe-2d74-4c40-8295-d728dac4f471.text: I'm in search of a quest.

d119d506-db1b-4ae2-8b96-11f004cb3996.title: Kaqemeex
d119d506-db1b-4ae2-8b96-11f004cb3996.text:
Hmm. I think I may have a worthwhile quest for you
actually. I don't know if you are familiar with the stone
circle south of Varrock or not, but...

0c3c2480-f48a-4a3c-b2b4-748977072a09.title: <player>
0c3c2480-f48a-4a3c-b2b4-748977072a09.text: Okay, I will try and help.

e2e71e68-61c5-4c07-9f87-fffc7db90a07.title: Kaqemeex
e2e71e68-61c5-4c07-9f87-fffc7db90a07.text:
Excellent. Go to the village south of this place and speak
to my fellow druid, Sanfew, who is working on the
purification ritual. He knows what is required to
complete it.

a29e09a8-0ffc-4fd6-8b86-c307dde8e82c.title: Kaqemeex
a29e09a8-0ffc-4fd6-8b86-c307dde8e82c.text:
Hello again, adventurer. You will need to speak to my
fellow druid Sanfew in the village south of here to
continue in your quest.

7756839e-d769-4aeb-bb93-d74a8dbda358.title: Kaqemeex
7756839e-d769-4aeb-bb93-d74a8dbda358.text:
I have word from Sanfew that you have been very
helpful in assisting him with his preparations for the
purification ritual. As promised I will now teach you the
ancient arts of Herblore.

db39e9e6-56f1-48fe-bd1c-43c3022665f8.title: Kaqemeex
db39e9e6-56f1-48fe-bd1c-43c3022665f8.text:
Herblore is the skill of working with herbs and other
ingredients, to make useful potions and poison.

7ba6f9f0-825b-49cf-9004-1bb40d70aca0.title: Kaqemeex
7ba6f9f0-825b-49cf-9004-1bb40d70aca0.text:
First you will need a vial, which can be found or made
with the crafting skill.

c2c16b1c-0897-4bad-87ed-da02b6a0d614.title: Kaqemeex
c2c16b1c-0897-4bad-87ed-da02b6a0d614.text:
Then you must gather the herbs needed to make the
potion you want.

42faf26d-4a92-4b0b-837a-49143f1f18fc.title: Kaqemeex
42faf26d-4a92-4b0b-837a-49143f1f18fc.text:
You must fill your vial with water and add the
ingredients you need. There are normally 2 ingredients
to each type of potion.

1a420f0a-e727-4a7f-a618-342ad0e3e7f2.title: Kaqemeex
1a420f0a-e727-4a7f-a618-342ad0e3e7f2.text:
Bear in mind, you must first clean each herb before
you can use it.

9b1f9952-0e42-4160-a86e-87e4330283fa.title: Kaqemeex
9b1f9952-0e42-4160-a86e-87e4330283fa.text:
You may also have to grind some ingredients before
you can use them. You will need a pestle and mortar
in order to do this.

850b4978-8720-4a37-9952-b774e6fe1a4f.title: Kaqemeex
850b4978-8720-4a37-9952-b774e6fe1a4f.text:
Herbs can be found on the ground, and are also
dropped by some monsters when you kill them.

47ddc0dc-6bf6-420a-a390-188483c9b9ed.title: Kaqemeex
47ddc0dc-6bf6-420a-a390-188483c9b9ed.text:
Let's try an example Attack potion: The first ingredient
is Guam leaf; the next is Eye of Newt.

b00700f0-862d-4a50-a77c-27941c9707d4.title: Kaqemeex
b00700f0-862d-4a50-a77c-27941c9707d4.text:
Mix these in your water-filled vial, and you will produce
an Attack potion. Drink this potion to increase your
Attack level.

02baaca3-99a4-48ae-9de3-4605debdbb48.title: Kaqemeex
02baaca3-99a4-48ae-9de3-4605debdbb48.text:
Different potions also require different Herblore levels
before you can make them.

e59e9bbb-868a-4cc4-9002-dbb77dd58179.title: Kaqemeex
e59e9bbb-868a-4cc4-9002-dbb77dd58179.text: Hello again. How is the Herblore going?

options.text: I need more practice at it...
Can you explain the fundamentals again?
What must I do to wear a Herblore skillcape?

02c5a1e2-b985-4271-addf-2b3f56ab3f55.title: <player>
02c5a1e2-b985-4271-addf-2b3f56ab3f55.text: What must I do to wear a Herblore skillcape?

43f43c8f-ac59-4656-b922-1e38217c116f.title: Kaqemeex
43f43c8f-ac59-4656-b922-1e38217c116f.text:
To earn the right to wear any skillcape you need to
have mastered that skill to the highest level possible and
it is no different for Herblore.

2a782b6d-7314-455e-8dc3-9919ffb88468.title: Kaqemeex
2a782b6d-7314-455e-8dc3-9919ffb88468.text:
With the cape equipped the Nardah Herbalist will create
unfinished potions for you and you may search the
cape for a pestle and mortar. When you have achieved
a level of 99, come back and talk to me again.

f6f0e82b-a227-4c05-9ef9-8975ad974d35.title: Kaqemeex
f6f0e82b-a227-4c05-9ef9-8975ad974d35.text:
Herblore is the skill of working with herbs and other
ingredients, to make useful potions and poison.

6d04ca4f-d88e-4978-9d04-f42bac8e8fba.title: Kaqemeex
6d04ca4f-d88e-4978-9d04-f42bac8e8fba.text:
First you will need a vial, which can be found or made
with the crafting skill.

e6635e51-301a-4bf0-8e79-1c7c6856c477.title: Kaqemeex
e6635e51-301a-4bf0-8e79-1c7c6856c477.text:
Then you must gather the herbs needed to make the
potion you want.

f0cf2ae0-a15c-41da-aa8b-90bafcd0d557.title: Kaqemeex
f0cf2ae0-a15c-41da-aa8b-90bafcd0d557.text:
You must fill your vial with water and add the
ingredients you need. There are normally 2 ingredients
to each type of potion.

22b94f35-9a6e-4f8a-aba3-8fffe4152e83.title: Kaqemeex
22b94f35-9a6e-4f8a-aba3-8fffe4152e83.text:
Bear in mind, you must first clean each herb before
you can use it.

0570914e-ffa0-4337-b5fc-8a0fbca60625.title: Kaqemeex
0570914e-ffa0-4337-b5fc-8a0fbca60625.text:
You may also have to grind some ingredients before
you can use them. You will need a pestle and mortar
in order to do this.

b3f92a26-7187-42c6-a12a-dedd1007afa6.title: Kaqemeex
b3f92a26-7187-42c6-a12a-dedd1007afa6.text:
Herbs can be found on the ground, and are also
dropped by some monsters when you kill them.

921c3809-4bc0-41ca-8b57-d8a4f438dc12.title: Kaqemeex
921c3809-4bc0-41ca-8b57-d8a4f438dc12.text:
Let's try an example Attack potion: The first ingredient
is Guam leaf; the next is Eye of Newt.

ee0b0106-0bb4-45a1-a852-cbb2962ed48e.title: Kaqemeex
ee0b0106-0bb4-45a1-a852-cbb2962ed48e.text:
Mix these in your water-filled vial, and you will produce
an Attack potion. Drink this potion to increase your
Attack level.

18779727-9a45-40e8-a3ad-c820c31a2fc3.title: Kaqemeex
18779727-9a45-40e8-a3ad-c820c31a2fc3.text:
Different potions also require different Herblore levels
before you can make them.

1f19cbe3-f8bf-4b0c-8f51-8a4afef94027.title: <player>
1f19cbe3-f8bf-4b0c-8f51-8a4afef94027.text: Can you explain the fundamentals again?

9c0b5587-ce98-4475-bbdd-cf42070f1624.title: Kaqemeex
9c0b5587-ce98-4475-bbdd-cf42070f1624.text:
Good luck with your Herblore practices, and a good day
to you.

15622f9f-309d-4519-9464-fd83c6475676.title: <player>
15622f9f-309d-4519-9464-fd83c6475676.text: I need more practice at it...
